sequenceDiagram
    participant App as ML Application<br/>/ Notebook
    participant OnlineSvc as feast-{name}-online<br/>6567/TCP HTTPS
    participant SecMgr as SecurityManager<br/>OIDC / K8s RBAC
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>Redis / PostgreSQL
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store<br/>BigQuery / DuckDB
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob<br/>ose-cli
    participant Operator as Feast Operator<br/>controller-manager
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over App,OnlineStore: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval

    App->>OnlineSvc: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTPS/TLS (service-serving certs)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC/K8s)
    OnlineSvc->>SecMgr: Validate token<br/>inject_user_details
    SecMgr->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (K8s auth mode)<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    K8sAPI-->>SecMgr: Token valid + user info
    SecMgr->>OIDC: JWKS retrieval (OIDC auth mode)<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>SecMgr: JWT validated
    SecMgr-->>OnlineSvc: RBAC: READ_ONLINE allowed
    OnlineSvc->>OnlineStore: Read features<br/>TCP/TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineSvc: Feature values
    OnlineSvc-->>App: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/TLS

    Note over CronJob,OnlineStore: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)

    CronJob->>OnlineSvc: POST /materialize<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: Intra-communication token
    OnlineSvc->>OfflineStore: Read historical features<br/>TCP/HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OfflineStore-->>OnlineSvc: Historical feature data
    OnlineSvc->>OnlineStore: Write materialized features<br/>TCP/TLS<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineSvc: Write confirmed
    OnlineSvc-->>CronJob: 200 OK

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Notebook ConfigMap Injection

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Notebook with<br/>opendatahub.io/feast-integration label
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read FeatureStore client ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: feature_store.yaml config
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {notebook}-feast-config ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ConfigMap created
